01/08/2003
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- Defence Minister Nikolai Svinarov acknowledged on Thursday (31 July) that the mission facing the Bulgarian contingent in Iraq carries a higher risk than any previous operation.
Answering journalists' questions, Svinarov said the unit Bulgaria is due to send would be deployed by mid-August, with full readiness expected by early September.
The first 30 servicemen left last weekend.
(BTA, Mediapool - 31/07/03)
